tachyon.master

Class MasterSource

  • java.lang.Object
    • tachyon.master.MasterSource
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Source

    public class MasterSource
extends Object
implements Source
    A MasterSource collects a Master's internal state. Metrics like *Ops are used to record how many times that operation was attempted so the counter is incremented no matter if it is successful or not.
